{"tid":189331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"案件審結警阻市民入𨋢 要求預留電梯","createTime":"2017-04-06T10:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T10:57:56.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f3a1c439b36b429c9678740937f379f461ddc77","tid":189331,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"又係差佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 保安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n區院姊妹花懷疑受騙案今日審結後，事主與兩名女親友一同離開。<span style=\"color: red;\">惟本案案件主管元朗警區重案組第3隊高級督察張俊朗，與另外數名警員在證人離開時，多次阻礙公眾人士進入升降機。其後，更向區院保安要求「reserve架𨋢畀我哋」</span>。保安雖拒絕，但開路讓警員及證人進入升降機，又向記者表示「你哋搭下架啦」。<br />\n<br />\n一名否認自己為警員、但一直與案件主管等人一同護送證人的男子，聲稱被人推撞受傷，當記者提出叫他報警求助時，他表示「咁又唔使」。他行經記者身旁時，突然爆出一句粗口「X你老母XX」，惟不知他所指何人。女事主與親友終由警方提供的客貨車送走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170406/s00001/1491474017059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170406%2Fs00001%2F1491474017059&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7f3ffe7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170406%2Fs00001%2F1491474017059&h=05eeb67c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170406/s00001/1491474017059</a>"}]}